---

<section
  class="py-24 bg-surface-dark border-t-0 border-b border-border-dark relative"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mb-16 text-center lg:text-left relative">
      <span
        class="text-primary font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 block"
        >Diagnóstico</span
      >
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white font-display mb-4">
        El problema de la mayoría <br /> de las landings
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-dim text-lg max-w-2xl font-light">
        Por qué tu web actual podría estar costándote clientes todos los días.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div
        class="group bg-background-dark border border-border-dark p-8 hover:border-white transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden rounded-sm hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <div
          class="mb-6 bg-surface-dark w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-border-dark group-hover:border-primary group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-6 h-6 text-text-light group-hover:text-primary"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="currentColor"
            aria-hidden="true"
            ><path
              d="M15 1H9v2h6V1zm-4 13h2V8h-2v6zm8.03-6.61l1.42-1.42c-.43-.51-.9-.99-1.41-1.41l-1.42 1.42C16.07 4.74 14.12 4 12 4c-4.97 0-9 4.03-9 9s4.03 9 9 9 9-4.03 9-9c0-2.12-.74-4.07-1.97-5.61zM12 20c-3.87 0-7-3.13-7-7s3.13-7 7-7 7 3.13 7 7-3.13 7-7 7z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Lentitud extrema</h3>
        <p class="text-text-dim text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Tus clientes no esperan. Si tu web tarda más de 3 segundos en cargar,
          el 53% se irá a la competencia antes de leer una palabra.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="group bg-background-dark border border-border-dark p-8 hover:border-white transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden rounded-sm hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <div
          class="mb-6 bg-surface-dark w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-border-dark group-hover:border-primary group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-6 h-6 text-text-light group-hover:text-primary"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="currentColor"
            aria-hidden="true"
            ><path
              d="M12 7c2.76 0 5 2.24 5 5 0 .65-.13 1.26-.36 1.83l2.92 2.92c1.51-1.26 2.7-2.89 3.43-4.75-1.73-4.39-6-7.5-11-7.5-1.4 0-2.74.25-3.98.7l2.16 2.16C10.74 7.13 11.35 7 12 7zM2 4.27l2.28 2.28.46.46C3.08 8.3 1.78 10.02 1 12c1.73 4.39 6 7.5 11 7.5 1.55 0 3.03-.3 4.38-.84l.42.42L19.73 22 21 20.73 3.27 3 2 4.27zM7.53 9.8l1.55 1.55c-.05.21-.08.43-.08.65 0 1.66 1.34 3 3 3 .22 0 .44-.03.65-.08l1.55 1.55c-.67.33-1.41.53-2.2.53-2.76 0-5-2.24-5-5 0-.79.2-1.53.53-2.2zm4.31-.78l3.15 3.15.02-.16c0-1.66-1.34-3-3-3l-.17.01z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Diseño genérico</h3>
        <p class="text-text-dim text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Plantillas de Wordpress que "se ven bonitas" pero no transmiten
          autoridad ni diferencian tu marca personal del resto.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="group bg-background-dark border border-border-dark p-8 hover:border-white transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden rounded-sm hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <div
          class="mb-6 bg-surface-dark w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-border-dark group-hover:border-primary group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-6 h-6 text-text-light group-hover:text-primary"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="currentColor"
            aria-hidden="true"
            ><path
              d="M21.5 14.98c-.02 0-.03 0-.05.01C21.2 13.3 19.76 12 18 12c-1.4 0-2.6.83-3.16 2.02C13.26 14.1 12 15.4 12 17c0 1.66 1.34 3 3 3h6.5c1.38 0 2.5-1.12 2.5-2.5s-1.12-2.52-2.5-2.52zM9.45 11.55l3.09-3.09 2.89 2.89c.79-.67 1.72-1.09 2.72-1.25-.34-3.3-3.15-5.89-6.56-5.89a6.5 6.5 0 00-6.5 6.28C2.87 10.73 1 12.75 1 15.2 1 17.85 3.15 20 5.8 20H6v-2h-.2C4.08 18 3 16.92 3 15.2c0-1.62 1.2-2.98 2.78-3.16l.9-.1.04-.9c.04-.8.34-1.54.83-2.15l1.3 1.3.6.6.6-.6z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Mensaje confuso</h3>
        <p class="text-text-dim text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Textos que hablan de ti ("somos líderes") en lugar de hablarle a los
          problemas y deseos de tu cliente ideal.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="group bg-background-dark border border-border-dark p-8 hover:border-white transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden rounded-sm hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <div
          class="mb-6 bg-surface-dark w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-border-dark group-hover:border-primary group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-6 h-6 text-text-light group-hover:text-primary"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="currentColor"
            aria-hidden="true"
            ><path
              d="M15 1c-1.65 0-3 1.35-3 3v4c0 1.65 1.35 3 3 3h3V5h2v6h2V4c0-1.65-1.35-3-3-3h-6zm0 2h4v4h-4V3zM2 4v7c0 1.65 1.35 3 3 3h3v4l4-4h2c1.65 0 3-1.35 3-3V7h-2v4c0 .55-.45 1-1 1h-2.59L9 15.59V12H5c-.55 0-1-.45-1-1V4H2z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Bajo retorno (ROI)</h3>
        <p class="text-text-dim text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Inviertes en anuncios de Facebook o Google, pero el tráfico llega a un
          "colador" donde pierdes el 90% de las oportunidades.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
